'''Minux Institute of Technology''' is a [[Nepal]]ese information technology training center located in [[Pokhara]], [[Nepal]]. Established in 2009, the organization offers courses in computer technology, as well as [[Information technology|IT]] products, web design and site hosting, and technical networking and computer maintenance support services. Classes offered include:

* Basic in Computer Application
* Diploma in Computer Application
* Advanced in Accounting Package
* Advanced in Graphics Designing
* Advanced in Webpage Design
* Advanced in Web Programming (PHP/MySQL)
* Advanced Hardward and Networking
* Advanced in Linux Administration
* Programming in (C/C++, QBasic, VB, Java, .NET, C#.NET, ASP.NET)
* Database Administration (MS-ACCESS, MySQL, MS-SQL Server, Oracle)
* Global Certification Course

